<HEADLINE>
<P>
FANS IN FIGHTING MOOD ABOUT KINGS-OILERS BRAWL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
So, owner Bruce McNall doesn't think that any fan who was at the Forum on Feb. 
28 was disappointed. I hate to break it to you Bruce, but as one who came to 
see a hockey game and saw a boxing match instead, I was disappointed. I didn't 
pay thousands of dollars for my season seats to see the game I love deteriorate 
into a street brawl. 
</P>
<P>
MICHELLE BUEHLER, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
