CONTROL; COAL MINING -- LABOR RELATIONS; COAL MINING -- LAYOFFS; MINERS -- 
WAGES AND SALARIES; MINING -- UNITED STATES; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
