<HEADLINE>
<P>
ABORTION PILL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As a native California woman, I was proud to learn that physicians of my state 
who met in Anaheim took a progressive stand on the abortion issue (State 
Medical Group Urges Tests of French Abortion Pill, March 6). 
</P>
<P>
I realize the manufacturer of this product has been harassed, much as women 
exercising their legal right to surgical abortions have been, but I hope the 
pharmaceutical company will show the courage these women have shown and begin 
procedures to market RU-486 in the United States. 
</P>
<P>
Availability of this product, that women can use in privacy, will help to take 
abortion out of the public and political arenas. 
</P>
<P>
MARTHA ABELL 
</P>
<P>
Seal Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
