<HEADLINE>
<P>
PREP ALL-LEAGUE TEAMS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BOYS' BASKETBALL 
</P>
<P>
ACADEMY LEAGUE 
</P>
<P>
First Team: Rob Hasty and Brad Pluckhan, Cal Lutheran; Steve Chappel, Liberty 
Christian; Dann Campaigne and Ryan Westendorf, St. Margaret's; Jacque Wright, 
St. Michael's. 
</P>
<P>
Second Team: Jeff Dumichina, Cal Lutheran; Art Andrews, Heritage; Trevor 
Durham, St. Margaret's; John Olerien and John Taylor, St. Michael's. 
</P>
<P>
MVP: Ryan Westendorf, St. Margaret's. Coach of the Year: Rick Bauer, St. 
Margaret's. 
</P>
<P>
ANGELUS LEAGUE 
</P>
<P>
First Team: Jason Green, Bishop Amat; Darrell Daniel and Kirk Jones, Bishop 
Montgomery; David Boyle, Andy Karich and Jason Quinn, Mater Dei; Brandon Ertle, 
St. Paul; Adam Anderson and Steve Marusich, Servite. 
</P>
<P>
Second Team: Jeff Martin, Bishop Amat; Joe Magyar and Pete Tolliver, Bishop 
Montgomery; Charlie Andres, Danny O'Neil and Derek Stone, Mater Dei; Edgar Diaz 
and Ryan Granillo, St. Paul; Mike Coady and Jamie Rosenkranz, Servite. 
</P>
<P>
MVP: Andy Karich, Mater Dei. 
</P>
<P>
CENTURY LEAGUE 
</P>
<P>
First Team: Abdi Barkhorder and Kevin Wilborn, Canyon; Greg Gottlieb and Jeff 
Leedom, El Modena; Fred Amos, Jeff Janis, Nick Konopisos and Mark Wilkinson, 
Foothill; Octavio Medina and Chauncy Woolridge, Santa Ana; George Alvarado, 
Santa Ana Valley; Chris Kirby, Villa Park. 
</P>
<P>
MVP: Fred Amos and Mark Wilkinson, Foothill. 
</P>
<P>
EMPIRE LEAGUE 
</P>
<P>
First Team: Jared Rice, Cypress; Mike Bradach and Jerome Facione, El Dorado; 
Joe Foss, Esperanza; Tes Whitlock, Loara; Robert Conlisk and Jason Cunningham, 
